Introduction

Jang Kyungho is the main dancer and sub-vocalist of the boy group TO1 under WAKEONE. He appeared in the show "World Klass" where he ranked 4th place, earning him a spot in the group.

Kyungho debuted as a member of TO1 on April 1, 2020, with their first mini album Reason for Being : Benevolence.

He is currently participating in the SBS reality show Universe League.
